abstract: The rare Orthodox Jew in the promoting ranks, Dmitriy Salita juggles fight preparation with the required hours off the grid just around prime fight time. His fighter just won a big match.
snippet: The rare Orthodox Jew in the promoting ranks, Dmitriy Salita juggles fight preparation with the required hours off the grid just around prime fight time. His fighter just won a big match.
lead_paragraph: ATLANTIC CITY — It was 22 ½ hours until the start of the biggest event of Dmitriy Salita’s career as a boxing promoter, the homestretch when he needed to make sure all of the kinks were ironed out: contracts, tickets, paychecks.

abstract: The Muse Brooklyn, a circus studio and event space in Bushwick, has three years to find a new home that will allow its students and performers to soar. (Literally.)
snippet: The Muse Brooklyn, a circus studio and event space in Bushwick, has three years to find a new home that will allow its students and performers to soar. (Literally.)
lead_paragraph: On a recent Friday night inside The Muse Brooklyn, a circus-arts studio housed in a mammoth warehouse in Bushwick, aspiring acrobats twirled from straps suspended from the 30-foot ceiling. Nearby, two young women were learning flips on a large hoop, called a German wheel, while instructors urged them on.

abstract: In this comedy by Will Arbery, three sisters slip-slide through time in a brightly heightened reality.
snippet: In this comedy by Will Arbery, three sisters slip-slide through time in a brightly heightened reality.
lead_paragraph: When white-haired Mary descends on her three daughters in Dallas for an impromptu visit, she brings them rosaries. Or she meant to, anyway; she can’t find them just this instant. What she does have handy is a morsel of guiding philosophy.

abstract: The total for Ms. Gillibrand, announced after many rivals disclosed their numbers, trails the amounts raised by the other five senators currently running for president.
snippet: The total for Ms. Gillibrand, announced after many rivals disclosed their numbers, trails the amounts raised by the other five senators currently running for president.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Senator Kirsten Gillibrand’s presidential campaign raised $3 million in the first quarter of the year, a spokeswoman said on Sunday, a disappointing sum that ranked her last among the six senators currently running for president.

abstract: The Vermont senator’s criticism of the Center for American Progress threatens to inflame the ideological divisions that roiled the Democratic Party in 2016.
snippet: The Vermont senator’s criticism of the Center for American Progress threatens to inflame the ideological divisions that roiled the Democratic Party in 2016.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Senator Bernie Sanders, in a rare and forceful rebuke by a presidential candidate of an influential party ally, has accused a liberal think tank of undermining Democrats’ chances of taking back the White House in 2020 by “using its resources to smear” him and other contenders pushing progressive policies.
